ppened immediately. And <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/top-7-players-can-replace-philippe-coutinho-liverpool/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Coutinho</a> transfer fee became the largest transfer fee for a player without release clause in their contract.</p>
