<p style="text-align: justify;">He could make his debut on Thursday in the Spanish Cup against Celta Vigo but will not able to play in the Champions League for Barcelona. So his presence will be important for La Liga and Copa del Rey.Â  <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/top-7-players-can-replace-philippe-coutinho-liverpool/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Coutinho</a> presence in the squad can replace Barcelona legend playmaker Andres Iniesta. Luis Suarez and <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/top-7-players-can-replace-philippe-coutinho-liverpool/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Coutinho</a> are going to play for the same clubs again, as a former teammate are considered very close on Merseyside. Barcelona spent <b>Â£</b>97m for Ousmane Dembele on last transfer window and now they offer Liverpool huge amount for <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/top-7-players-can-replace-philippe-coutinho-liverpool/">Philippe Coutinho</a>. It is the highest fee for a player sold by an English club and that is also a record.Â  Liverpool club is searching for a talent to replace <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/top-7-players-can-replace-philippe-coutinho-liverpool/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Philippe Coutinho</a> and Monacoâ€™s Thomas Lemar is their main target. <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/france-road-russia-fifa-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">France</a> international Thomas Lemar wonders all with his amazing move and skills but Ligue 1 club are unwilling to sell in this transfer window. Recently Liverpool signed defender Virgil van Dijk from Southampton for <b>Â£</b>75m.<img class="aligncenter wp-image-836" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/cautino-to-barca-198x300.jpg" alt="" width="301" height="456" /></p>
